Date: 29-07-2025

Aim
To model a ride booking using a class with id, name, and distance.
To compute fare with base fare and per-km charges.
To apply 10% discount when distance > 20 km and display results.
Algorithm
Read N (number of bookings).
For each booking, read bookingId (int), customerName (String), distance (double).
Compute fare = 50 + 10 * distance.
If distance > 20, apply 10% discount on fare.
Round final fare to one decimal place for display.
Print booking details in the specified format.
Repeat for all bookings.
Program (Java)
import java.util.*;
class Booking {
    private int bookingId;
    private String customerName;
    private double distance;
    public Booking(int bookingId, String customerName, double distance) {
        this.bookingId = bookingId;
        this.customerName = customerName;
        this.distance = distance;
    }
    public void setBookingId(int bookingId){ this.bookingId = bookingId; }
    public void setCustomerName(String customerName){ this.customerName = customerName; }
    public void setDistance(double distance){ this.distance = distance; }
    public int getBookingId(){ return bookingId; }
    public String getCustomerName(){ return customerName; }
    public double getDistance(){ return distance; }
    public double finalFare(){
        double fare = 50 + 10 * distance;
        if (distance > 20) fare *= 0.9;
        return fare;
    }
}
public class CityCab {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = Integer.parseInt(sc.nextLine().trim());
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int id = Integer.parseInt(sc.nextLine().trim());
            String name = sc.nextLine();
            double dist = Double.parseDouble(sc.nextLine().trim());
            Booking b = new Booking(id, name, dist);
            System.out.println("Booking ID: " + b.getBookingId());
            System.out.println("Customer Name: " + b.getCustomerName());
            System.out.printf("Final Fare: %.1f%n", b.finalFare());
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}


Sample Output
Booking ID: 5678
Final Fare: 270.0
Result
Implemented encapsulation with getters/setters for booking data.
Calculated and displayed discounted fare as per business rule.
